Exact String Match

Source: vignettes/rmd/exact-string-match.Rmd
exact-string-match.Rmd
library(pg13)
conn <- localConnect(dbname = "athena",
                     port = 5432)
#> Connecting using PostgreSQL driver
searchTable(conn = conn,
            schema = "omop_vocabulary",
            tableName = "concept",
            values = "Aspirin",
            case_insensitive = TRUE)
